00:00:51.017 --> 00:00:52.285 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: <i>After the weekend had passed,</i>

00:00:52.352 --> 00:00:54.187 line:5%,start
I really felt
like I needed to call Abby

00:00:54.254 --> 00:00:55.755 line:95%,end
<i>so that we could clear the air.</i>

