00:01:04.130 --> 00:01:06.466 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: <i>Seeing how Abby</i>
<i>gave her favorite, Maddie,</i>

00:01:06.533 --> 00:01:09.035 line:95%,end
<i>two solos last week,</i>
<i>I think I had a right to be upset.</i>

00:01:09.102 --> 00:01:10.370 line:95%,end
I think I deserve
an apology, too.

00:01:10.437 --> 00:01:12.672 line:95%,end
But, you know what?
I'll be the bigger woman.

00:01:15.675 --> 00:01:17.377 line:95%,end
Hello.
You wanted to see me?

00:01:17.444 --> 00:01:18.478 line:95%,end
Yes.

00:01:18.545 --> 00:01:20.713 line:95%,end
Abby, I came here
to try to make amends with you.

00:01:22.749 --> 00:01:24.784 line:95%,end
I cannot let you
on my property

00:01:25.985 --> 00:01:28.822 line:95%,end
