00:01:28.888 --> 00:01:30.757 line:95%,end
You need to sign this.
I need to go back to work.

00:01:30.824 --> 00:01:33.326 line:95%,end
Abby, I was out of line,
the way I behaved in that room.

00:01:33.393 --> 00:01:37.630 line:95%,end
